in the dashboard, click on "new item"
freestyle project
add a new build step

export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-amd64
export MAVEN_HOME=/opt/maven
export GRADLE_HOME=/opt/gradle
export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$MAVEN_HOME/bin:$GRADLE_HOME/bin:$PATH

echo "JAVA_HOME is $JAVA_HOME"
java -version

echo "Maven version:"
mvn -version

echo "Gradle version:"
gradle -v

git -version

find some already existing maven project, like 2nd. If there's none, create a new default maven project. and paste the pom.xml from github)
cd (the location of the above project)

mvn test

Save

Build Now.
 it should run successfully and tick mark should be visible.

 finished.

